	<h2>Determining Appropriate Fee for Industrial Radiation Machines</h2>
	<p>An application for a certificate of registration shall be accompanied by a two year non-refundable administrative fee. Fee payments by check or money order shall be made payable to <em>Texas Department of State Health Services</em>. In the case of a certificate of registration that authorizes more than one category of use, the total fee is the category with the highest corresponding fee. Additional authorized use location(s) under the same registration are an additional 30% of the applicable fee.</p>
